data.description: 🏡 Discover the ultimate family haven in West Palm, FL! Nestled in a gated community, this 3 bed, 2.5 bath gem is a dream come true. Embrace the community spirit with HOA perks and a refreshing public pool. Convenience is key with nearby I-91, a treasure trove of restaurants, and the convenience of Publix Grocery. Create memories in this family-friendly haven that seamlessly blends comfort and style. Your new chapter starts here - welcome home! 🏊‍♂️🍔🛒 #WestPalmLiving
